Contractor: {{contractor_name}}
Address: {{contractor_address}}
Phone: {{contractor_phone}}
Maryland Home Improvement Commission (MHIC) License Number: {{license_number}}

All home improvement contractors in Maryland must be licensed by the Maryland Home Improvement Commission. If you have questions about this contractor's license, contact MHIC at (410) 230-6309 or visit www.dllr.state.md.us/license/mhic.

If a salesperson solicited or negotiated this contract, their name and MHIC Salesperson Registration Number must appear here:

Salesperson Name: {{salesperson_name}}
MHIC Salesperson Registration Number: {{salesperson_reg_number}}

RIGHT TO CANCEL

You may cancel this contract within three business days after the date you sign it. To cancel, send written notice by certified mail or hand delivery to:

{{contractor_name}}
{{contractor_address}}

If you cancel within three business days, the contractor must return any deposit you paid within 15 days.

FEDERAL NOTICE OF RIGHT TO CANCEL

You have the right under federal law to cancel this transaction within three business days of signing. To cancel, notify us in writing at:
{{contractor_name}}, {{contractor_address}}

Date of transaction: {{contract_date}}
